notesStmt.note: Title supplied by cataloger; alternate title Somerāmāṃḍārabhāṣya from colophon (f. 287v); title abbreviated as Prayoga throughout, upper right verso.
287 leaves foliated 1-287, upper left and lower right verso, often with hundred numeral dropped.
Mistakes covered over in yellow, white, or blacked out; some corrections in margins.

msIdentifier.repository: Kislak Center for Special Collections, Rare Books and Manuscripts

msContents.summary: Contains the sub-commentary (tīkā) of Kauśikarāma on Dhūrtasvāmin's commentary (bhāṣya) of the Āpastambaśrautasūtra, an ancient text on ritual sacrifice.

msItem.title: Dhūrtasvāmibhāṣyatīkā
धूर्तस्वामिभाष्यतीका
msItem.colophon: Colophon: saptamaḥ paṭalaḥ // samāptaḥ praśnaḥ // somerāmāṃḍārabhāṣyaṃ // idaṃ pustakaṃ rājārāmabhaṭṭaṃ nagara[ṃ] // vāstavyaṃ śrīkā[ś]ikṣetraṃ ase // paropakārārtha // madhubhaṭṭena cātudhāreṇa likhitaṃ saṃnyāsiṃ // śrīrāmārpaṇamṃastu // 5694 // saṃ[va]t 1887 // vikramāśake pravaṃganāmaṃ savato uttarāyaṇe caiṃtraśudha 5 pacamītraddani samāṃpta śubhabhavatu // śaka 1752 // (f. 287v).

history.provenance: Formerly owned by Rājārāmabhaṭṭa who lived in Vārānasi (f. 287v).
